description: This great Asian Fusion food truck is serving both classic and unique new creations of mixed culture dishes, incorporating Japanese, Korean, Thai, Chinese, and American Food! Ms. Fu shares her joy and love of food with everyone at many events; fairs, farmer's markets, horse shows, private parties in New Jersey and Pennsylvania. If you're hungry for some amazing new takes on Asian cuisine, stop by Ms. Fu's! You're in for a treat.
name: Ms. Fu's Yummy Food Truck
